=== 退役 ===
2007年春，[[世界气象组织|世界气象组织]]将“伊欧凯”从中北太平洋风暴名单中退役，并以“艾欧帕”（{{lang|en|Iopa}}）替换<ref>{{cite web | author = Dennis H. McCarthy | year = 2007 | title = National Weather Service Instruction Tropical Cyclone Names and Pronunciation Guide | accessdate = 2014-09-25 | url = http://www.nws.noaa.gov/directives/sym/pd01006006curr.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131017013743/http://www.nws.noaa.gov/directives/sym/pd01006006curr.pdf | deadurl = no | format = PDF | archivedate = 2013-10-17 }}</ref>。夏威夷州民防部门还在第61届跨部门飓风会议上提出，飓风丹尼尔已经造成了很大的威胁和损失，因此请求将其名称退役<ref>{{cite web |publisher=Interdepartmental Hurricane Conference |year=2007 |title=The Nation's Hurricane Program: An Interagency Success Story |accessdate=2013-04-02 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.ofcm.gov/ihc07/web-61st-IHC-Booklet.pdf |format=PDF |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130402172811/http://www.ofcm.gov/ihc07/web-61st-IHC-Booklet.pdf |archivedate=2013-04-02 }}</ref>。但世界气象组织没有同意这项请求<ref name="name" />。

